<metainfo>
  <schemaVersion>2.0</schemaVersion>
  <services>
    <service>
      <name>YARN</name>
      <displayName>YARN</displayName>
      <version>2.6.0.2.2</version>
      <comment>YARN(Yet Another Resource Negotiator)：用于Hadoop 2.0的通用资源管理系统，可为上层应用提供统一的资源管理和调度</comment>
      <components>
        <component>
          <name>APP_TIMELINE_SERVER</name>
          <cardinality>1</cardinality>
        </component>
      </components>
      
      <osSpecifics>
        <osSpecific>
          <osFamily>redhat5,redhat6,suse11</osFamily>
          <packages>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop_2_2_*-yarn</name>
            </package>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop_2_2_*-mapreduce</name>
            </package>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop_2_2_*-hdfs</name>
            </package>
          </packages>
        </osSpecific>
        <osSpecific>
          <osFamily>ubuntu12</osFamily>
          <packages>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop-2-2-.*-yarn</name>
            </package>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop-2-2-.*-mapreduce</name>
            </package>
          </packages>
        </osSpecific>
      </osSpecifics>
    </service>

    <service>
      <name>MAPREDUCE2</name>
      <displayName>MapReduce2</displayName>
      <version>2.6.0.2.2</version>
      <comment>Hadoop下一代 MapReduce计算引擎：基于Map和Reduce的编程模型，对大规模数据集进行并行运算</comment>
      <osSpecifics>
        <osSpecific>
          <osFamily>redhat5,redhat6,suse11</osFamily>
          <packages>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop_2_2_*-mapreduce</name>
            </package>
          </packages>
        </osSpecific>
        <osSpecific>
          <osFamily>ubuntu12</osFamily>
          <packages>
            <package>
              <name>hadoop-2-2-.*-mapreduce</name>
            </package>
          </packages>
        </osSpecific>
      </osSpecifics>
      <configuration-dir>configuration-mapred</configuration-dir>

    </service>

  </services>
</metainfo>
